Trade/Device Name(s): Access 25(OH) Vitamin D Total for use on the UniCel DxI Immunoassay System
Access 25(OH) Vitamin D Total Calibrators for use on the UniCel DxI Immunoassay System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Access 25(OH) Vitamin D Total assay and calibrators for quantitative determination of 25-hydroxyvitamin D using UniCel DxI Immunoassay System
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative determination of total 25-hydroxyvitamin D levels in human serum and plasma using the UniCel DxI Immunoassay Systems to aid in the assessment of vitamin D sufficiency
